-- Oakland Athletics Pitcher Ben Sheets Is Out for Season With Elbow Injury
-- Jay Beberman
-- 2010-07-29T12:53:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/oakland-athletics-pitcher-ben-sheets-is-out-for-season-with-elbow-injury.html

          
          
             Oakland Athletics pitcher Ben Sheets
will miss the remainder of the season with a torn tendon in his
right elbow, the Major League Baseball team said.  
 Sheets, 32, signed a one-year, $10 million contract with
Oakland in January.  
 Sheets has a career record of 90 wins and 92 losses over
nine seasons with Oakland and the Milwaukee Brewers.  
          
          


  


        